    skip( "need DBD::AnyData and Class::DBI to test syntax auto-detection", 7 ) if $@;

=for notes

    LimitOffset     PostgreSQL, MySQL (recent), SQLite
    LimitXY         MySQL (older)
    LimitYX         SQLite (optional)
    RowsTo          InterBase/FireBird

    Top             SQL/Server, MS Access
    RowNum          Oracle
